<section class="about-section container">
  <div class="about-grid">
    <div class="about-text">
      <div class="section-num">04</div>
      <h2>ABOUT MARCHIVE</h2>
      <p>Marchive adalah ruang arsip digital tempat beragam karya dikumpulkan, disusun, dan dibagikan. Dari tulisan, puisi, hingga desain—semuanya bagian dari perjalanan berpikir dan berkarya.</p>
      <a href="#" class="read-more">READ MORE &rarr;</a>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image">
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1549490349-8643362247b5?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=1000" alt="Archway" />
    </div>
    <div class="footer-branded">
      <h3>MARCHIVE</h3>
      <p class="est">EST. 2024</p>
      <div class="footer-motto">“We don't just create. We preserve what matters.”</div>
      <div class="footer-icons">
         <!-- Social icons -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-section {
    padding: 150px 0;
  }

  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 40px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .about-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }

  .read-more {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--accent-color);
    padding-bottom: 5px;
  }

  .about-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 600px;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .footer-branded {
    padding-top: 50px;
  }

  .footer-branded h3 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .footer-motto {
    font-style: italic;
    opacity: 0.6;
    margin: 30px 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .about-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
